reviewText: Received order quickly and packaged well. Amazon description precise. My purchase is exactly as described. Would order again and would recommend to a friend.
I LOVE XXX STATE OF THE UNION, HAVE WATCHED IT MANY MANY TIMES.  ANACONDA IS ALSO A GOOD MOVIE THAT I HAVE WATCHED MANY TIMES. GHOST OF MARS IS AN OK MOVIE AND HAVE WATCHED IT A FEW TIMES.
Bought mostly for Anaconda, but figured best buy for your money to get 3 movies instead of jus the one. Ghost of Mars is a weird movie...FYI. lol, and we all know XXX.
my friend loves ice cube so what better way to make her happy than with this 3 pack of movies

Who doesn't love Ice Cube? To be honest, I ordered it for Ghosts of Mars, but getting Anaconda and State of the Union was a plus! It was a great price and the product arrived in great condition (& quick too).
